Date: Wed, 4 Sep 2024 16:17:28 +0800
Subject: ionic: Convert comma to semicolon
Patch-mainline: v6.12-rc1
Git-commit: 62c9f50eabe080cb07ed5e6c55d1fd38ad04201b
References: jsc#PED-11379

Replace comma between expressions with semicolons.

Using a ',' in place of a ';' can have unintended side effects.
Although that is not the case here, it is seems best to use ';'
unless ',' is intended.

Found by inspection.
No functional change intended.
Compile tested only.

Signed-off-by: Chen Ni <nichen@iscas.ac.cn>
Reviewed-by: Shannon Nelson <shannon.nelson@amd.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20240904081728.1353260-1-nichen@iscas.ac.cn
Signed-off-by: Jakub Kicinski <kuba@kernel.org>
Acked-by: Thomas Bogendoerfer <tbogendoerfer@suse.de>
